OL,3,CWho is Darragh Mackin? The solicitor
OL,4,Cbacking the Summerland campaign
OL,6,FA prominent human rights solicitor
OL,7,Ffrom Northern Ireland has announced he
OL,8,Fwill be backing the 'Justice for
OL,9,FSummerland' campaign.
OL,11,FDarragh Mackin has written to the
OL,12,Fisland's attorney general, outlining
OL,13,Fthe campaign's intention to apply for
OL,14,Fa fresh inquest into the Summerland
OL,15,Ffire.
OL,17,FLast month, Darragh successfully
OL,18,Foverturned the verdicts of 48 people
OL,19,Fwho died in the Stardust nightclub
OL,20,Ffire 43 years ago.
