OL,3,CWho is Darragh Mackin? The solicitor
OL,4,Cbacking the Summerland campaign
OL,6,FFollowing on from this success, he
OL,7,Fwill now represent the Summerland
OL,8,Ffamilies, fighting to overturn the
OL,9,F'death by misadventure' verdict given
OL,10,Fto all 50 who died.
OL,12,FMr Mackin has written to the Isle of
OL,13,FMan's attorney general on behalf of
OL,14,Fthe 'Justice for Summerland' campaign,
OL,15,Finforming him of their intention to
OL,16,Fapply for a fresh inquest.
OL,18,FHe said: "Summerland families have now
OL,19,Fformally contacted the attorney
OL,20,Fgeneral to notify him of their
OL,21,Fintention to apply for a fresh inquest.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/11
