OL,3,CWho is Darragh Mackin? The solicitor
OL,4,Cbacking the Summerland campaign
OL,6,F"In an almost identical set of
OL,7,Fcircumstances with the Stardust, a
OL,8,Ffresh inquest, we say, can, through
OL,9,Fthe right mechanism, call witnesses,
OL,10,Fhear expert evidence, and establish
OL,11,Fthe truth."
OL,13,FMr Mackin said his initial reaction to
OL,14,Freading the verdict was 'utmost
OL,15,Fconcerning', adding that when he
OL,16,Flooked at how the verdict was decided,
OL,17,Fhe was 'exceptionally concerned'.
