OL,3,CWho is Darragh Mackin? The solicitor
OL,4,Cbacking the Summerland campaign
OL,6,FHe has described the Summerland
OL,7,Fdisaster as 'one of the greatest
OL,8,Fmiscarriages of justice on these
OL,9,Fisles', adding that the verdict is
OL,10,F'wholly unreflective of the evidence'.
OL,12,FHe said: "When we look at the set of
OL,13,Ffacts and we look at they indeed even
OL,14,Fthe inquiry report, this goes much
OL,15,Ffurther and beyond that of an accident
OL,16,F- and that is why the families feel
OL,17,Fvery, very strong that the verdict is
OL,18,Findeed the wrong one."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
