OL,3,CWho is Darragh Mackin? The solicitor
OL,4,Cbacking the Summerland campaign
OL,6,F"I think that's absolutely correct,
OL,7,Fbecause what we can tell now, even on
OL,8,Fany kind of cursory examination of the
OL,9,Fevidence, is that through expert
OL,10,Fevidence, much more detail could be
OL,11,Ffound, and indeed the truth could be
OL,12,Festablished."
OL,14,FMr Mackin has called on the Isle of
OL,15,FMan to 'take action', as the campaign
OL,16,Fmoves to reopen the inquest into the
OL,17,FSummerland fire.
