OL,3,CWho is Darragh Mackin? The solicitor
OL,4,Cbacking the Summerland campaign
OL,6,FHe said: "The message to the Isle of
OL,7,FMan Government is very simple: We must
OL,8,Flearn lessons from the other parts of
OL,9,Fthe Isles where we've seen for
OL,10,Fexample, in Hillsborough, Ballymurphy,
OL,11,Fthe Stardust, we've seen on many
OL,12,Foccasions where failed investigations
OL,13,Fhave been remedied through an
OL,14,Feffective investigation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/11
