OL,3,CWho is Darragh Mackin? The solicitor
OL,4,Cbacking the Summerland campaign
OL,6,F"It's simply not enough to do nothing.
OL,7,FWe must take action and the action
OL,8,Fmust be a fresh investigation because
OL,9,Fthat investigation in itself can bring
OL,10,Fand help these families with closure
OL,11,Fand can help give them a pathway to
OL,12,Fjustice."
OL,14,FIt comes after the Chief Minister
OL,15,Fapologised for the 'pain, harm and
OL,16,Ffailings' of the disaster, during a
OL,17,Fsitting of Tynwald in July 2023.
OL,19,FThis was followed by a national
OL,20,Fservice of remembrance for the 50th
OL,21,Fanniversary in August.
