OL,3,CWho is Darragh Mackin? The solicitor
OL,4,Cbacking the Summerland campaign
OL,6,FDarragh Mackin was a leading voice in
OL,7,Fthe campaign to overturn the verdicts
OL,8,Fof the 48 people who died in the
OL,9,FStardust fire in Dublin in 1981.
OL,11,FAn initial inquiry into the Stardust
OL,12,Ftragedy found that 'arson' was the
OL,13,Flikely cause of the fire, but this was
OL,14,Flater quashed, kickstarting a campaign
OL,15,Ffor justice as fresh inquests were
OL,16,Fordered.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
