OL,3,CWho is Darragh Mackin? The solicitor
OL,4,Cbacking the Summerland campaign
OL,6,FThis led to a new inquest opening on
OL,7,F25 April 2023, where a jury heard how
OL,8,Fmany fire exits were locked, chained
OL,9,For obstructed - mirroring various
OL,10,Feyewitness accounts at Summerland.
OL,12,FThe campaign ended with conclusive
OL,13,Fverdicts of 'unlawful killing' -
OL,14,Fsuccessfully overturning the original
OL,15,Finquest verdict after 40 years.
OL,17,FHe said: "The similarities between the
OL,18,FSummerland and the Stardust are
OL,19,Fstriking.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
